Description:
flock(2) function: advisory file locks.

Files:
lib/flock.c
m4/flock.m4

Depends-on:
sys_file
msvc-nothrow    [test $HAVE_FLOCK = 0]

configure.ac:
gl_FUNC_FLOCK
if test $HAVE_FLOCK = 0; then
  AC_LIBOBJ([flock])
  gl_PREREQ_FLOCK
fi
gl_HEADER_SYS_FILE_MODULE_INDICATOR([flock])

Makefile.am:

Include:
<sys/file.h>

